        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Accounting STEM Pursuit Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill authorizes states and local educational agencies (LEAs) to use grant funds provided through the Student Support and Academic Enrichment Program for accounting education. In particular, LEAs may use these grant funds to implement programs to teach accounting, including by increasing access to high-quality accounting courses through 12th grade for students who are members of underrepresented groups.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
